      • buildAll

        public Map<String,Object> buildAll()
                            throws AISPException
        Run the script and extract the named variables.
        Returns:
        a map of objects of the class and optional names created in the script keyed by the names provided to the constructor. On successful return, the map contains objects of the type/class specified in the constructor.
